        <div class="hc-card-desc">Generating and exporting reports for tasks, attendance, and more</div>
      </div>
      <i class="bi bi-arrow-up-right hc-card-arrow"></i>
    </a>
    <a href="/help?topic=drive" target="_blank" class="hc-card" style="--hc-accent:#3b82f6;--hc-rgb:59,130,246" data-title="Google Drive">
      <div class="hc-card-icon"><i class="bi bi-cloud-arrow-up-fill"></i></div>
      <div class="hc-card-body">
